        <mxCell id="secBox" value="SEGURANÇA&#xa;• Microsoft Defender for Cloud (CSPM/CWP)&#xa;• Microsoft Sentinel (SIEM/SOAR)&#xa;• Entra ID: MFA, Conditional Access, Zero Trust&#xa;• Key Vault (segredos/chaves) + criptografia&#xa;• Azure Firewall Premium + WAF + DDoS&#xa;• NSGs, Private Endpoints, sem IP público em VMs" style="rounded=6;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FBE9E9;strokeColor=#D13438;fontColor=#7A1416;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
