        <mxCell id="costBox" value="GESTÃO DE CUSTOS&#xa;• Azure Cost Management + Billing&#xa;• Budgets, alertas e anomalias&#xa;• Reservations + Savings Plans (estáveis)&#xa;• VMSS / autoscale (cargas elásticas)&#xa;• Right-sizing via Azure Advisor&#xa;• FinOps + Comitê de Custos (fatura → API → CFM)" style="rounded=6;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF4E5;strokeColor=#D9822B;fontColor=#7A4A12;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
